title: 9: Performance Hacks with Dave Asprey
description:
In this episode, I sit down with my friend Dave Asprey. Dave is the CEO of Bulletproof, inventor of Bulletproof Coffee, and author of the new book “Head Strong.” Dave shares some of his best performance hacks for getting and staying ready, alert, and focused.
